                <li>UI feels dated, learning curve steep</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Veteran SEOs who rely on Trust Flow as a quality signal.</div>
            <a href="https://majestic.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">10</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Moz Link Explorer</div>
